MsoPlainText\">Thank you for visiting our web site.&nbsp; When you registered, you indicated that we should contact you via e-mail and this message is in response to that request.&nbsp;\n<o:p></o:p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoPlainText\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoPlainText\">If you have questions about our products or services, we can certainly answer them for you.&nbsp; Please let us know if you&#8217;re interested in having a discussion over the phone and when would be the best day and time to reach you.<o:p></o:p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoPlainText\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoPlainText\">Thank you for your time, interest and consideration.&nbsp; We look forward to speaking with you soon.<o:p></o:p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoPlainText\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoPlainText\">Sincerely,<o:p></o:p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Manu Goyal, CFA<o:p></o:p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding:3.75pt 11.25pt 3.75pt 0in\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%\"><img width=\"187\" height=\"55\" id=\"Picture_x0020_1\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,\" alt=\"cid:image001.gif@01C9F95E.9ACF9FF0\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;color:#1F497D\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border:none;border-left:solid #00234C 1.0pt;padding:3.75pt 15.0pt 3.75pt 15.0pt\">\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%\"><b><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#00234C\">Manu Goyal, CFA<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;color:#404040\">Director - Business Development<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:115%\"><a href=\"mailto:m